attribute_description: Rate category based on time of day, 'off peak' 9pm-7am, 'shoulder' 7am-3pm, 'peak' 3pm-9pm. Using weekday shoulder use (7am to 3pm), weekend shoulder hours differ (7am to 9pm).
Variable cost of electricity per kWh for corresponding time of day (cents).
Fixed cost of electiricity, is constant all day (cents).
